originalText.text: Dr.Holly Weiner has been a great provider for countless years for me! I been seeing her since senior year in high school. I been out of HS for 8 years now and currently carrying my first child. She has done a tremendous job, with my health as I have a lot of complications. She always respects all my decisions and always recommends great things for me. She’s very knowledgeable and experienced, I highly recommend her. I have moved far away and still remain in this clinic because of her services. She’s a 10/10 !
